headline: Invesco Canada announces cash distributions for its ETFs
summary: Invesco Canada Ltd. ("Invesco") announced today the June 2025 distributions for its exchange-traded funds (ETFs). Unitholders of record on June 27, 2025, will receive cash distributions payable on July 8, 2025.

headline: The Dollar Is Hanging On to Its Haven Role by a Thread, Survey Shows
summary: (Bloomberg) -- The escalating Middle East conflict is likely to help the dollar hold on to its haven role — but only just, the latest Bloomberg Pulse survey shows.
